    "ai-tha-ap533:24.2_0": "he is the Holy One,",
    "ai-tha-ap533:24.3_0": "When I canceled my home",
    "ai-tha-ap533:24.4_0": "Sumana, Sujāta,",
    "ai-tha-ap533:25.1_0": "My defilements have been burnt away by practicing absorption—",
    "ai-tha-ap533:25.2_0": "rebirth into all states of existence is eradicated,",
